content.rendered:
The Greater Los Angeles African-American Chamber of Commerce (GLAAACC) recently hosted their 22nd Annual Economic Awards Dinner. These awards are presented to the companies and individuals who have contributed to economic growth and development of the African-American community in Los Angeles.

Alticor Inc’ Southern California Distirct Project Development Manager, Andy Millar was presented the “Special Recognition Award” for contribution and assistance to minority businesses within the Greater Los Angeles area.
